<p>It is the first time that World Walking Day event was held in Hangzhou on 
June 5th. As that day is the World 

Environment Day, many participants 
aimed to engaging in walking to foster environmental friendly and low carbon 
values. Around 6000 citizens took 

part in this 5 kilometers long event.   </p><p>Many participants said, "Hangzhou is always regarded as a scenic 
wonderland, and we should 

encourage more citizens to participating in walking, 
one of the green life styles, so as to make the city more beautiful. During the 
5 kilometers 

walking, they not only got the right scientific exercising methods, 
but also react positively to this year World Environment Day's theme. Moreover, 


the participants took the environmental friendly bags, bottles and 
handkerchiefs, instead of disposable paper cup and tissues. Many citizens who 


used to drive to work attended this event as well. They said, "Hangzhou suffers 
from the increasingly serious traffic congestion problem day by 

day, and the 
environment is getting worse and worse, as a result, we and the society would 
derive substantial benefits, if we walked more or drove 

less."</p><p></p>